        <mxCell id="mgi4BZDg1edCQAZwwnGo-2" value="&lt;font style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot; face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;DWT 是CTERX-M里面的内核外设&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;32位的计数器是向上计数的模式CCYCCNT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot; face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;一般是由主频1/systemclock，这是内核心跳一次&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;假设system clock是72M那么一次跳动就是14ns&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;strokeColor=none;align=left;fillColor=none;html=1;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=20;fontFamily=Architects Daughter;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DArchitects%2BDaughter;labelBackgroundColor=none;" parent="1" vertex="1">
