        <mxCell id="lRMUmvbayZdvGjP5ZWLq-31" value="队列扩展&lt;div&gt;1.通过传递变量地址的形式,来加快数据的搬运。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2.邮箱形式&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Lucida Console;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="828" y="1594" width="725" height="49" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Dc-kJc3XikHqwO9CGs-W-1" value="1.存储指针的队列&lt;div&gt;首先为什么会有这种需求&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1.究其原因是因为rtos的队列内部机制是字节复制形式,来存储到队列和读出队列，当数据量很大那么就得不偿失，会有2次数据的拷贝&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;所以通过存储指针的方式来减少大数据的传递机制。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2.使用时一定要保证数据的有效性,不能两边都读或写,这样数据会很危险，因为拿到的数据是对方的指针&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3.使用时务必确保传递的指针有效性,防止空指针&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4.使用实例：&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(77,77,76);&quot;&gt;xQueue2 = xQueueCreate( &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(245,135,31);&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(77,77,76);&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(137,89,168);&quot;&gt;sizeof&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(77,77,76);&quot;&gt;( &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(137,89,168);&quot;&gt;char&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(77,77,76);&quot;&gt; * ) );&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(77,77,76);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(137,89,168);&quot;&gt;const char&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(77,77,76);&quot;&gt; * &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(137,89,168);&quot;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(77,77,76);&quot;&gt; pcMessage = &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(113,140,0);&quot;&gt;&quot;Message from vSenderTask1\r\n&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(77,77,76);&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(77,77,76);&quot;&gt;xQueueSend( xQueue1, &amp;amp;pcMessage, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(245,135,31);&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(77,77,76);&quot;&gt; );&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(77,77,76);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(77,77,76);&quot;&gt;xQueueReceive( xQueueThatContainsData, &amp;amp;pcReceivedString, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(245,135,31);&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-size:10.4276pt;font-family:&#39;Consolas&#39;;color:rgb(77,77,76);&quot;&gt; );&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Consolas&quot; color=&quot;#4d4d4c&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.9035px;&quot;&gt;通过上述的方法可以大大减少传递时间,注意：在&amp;amp;指针的地址的时候产生的是2级指针的形式,这样就能通过传递参数来修改指针的内容,以此来达到访问的目的&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Lucida Console;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="827" y="1666" width="725" height="309" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Dc-kJc3XikHqwO9CGs-W-2" value="&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;2.邮箱形式&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 10.4276pt; font-family: Consolas; color: rgb(77, 77, 76);&quot;&gt;xMailbox = xQueueCreate( &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 10.4276pt; font-family: Consolas; color: rgb(245, 135, 31);&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 10.4276pt; font-family: Consolas; color: rgb(77, 77, 76);&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 10.4276pt; font-family: Consolas; color: rgb(137, 89, 168);&quot;&gt;sizeof&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 10.4276pt; font-family: Consolas; color: rgb(77, 77, 76);&quot;&gt;( Example_t ) ); 长度为1的队列&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(77, 77, 76); font-family: Consolas; font-size: 10.4276pt; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;并且在rtos的官方文档里推荐使用&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 10.4276pt; font-family: Consolas; color: rgb(77, 77, 76);&quot;&gt;BaseType_t &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 10.4276pt; font-family: Consolas; color: rgb(66, 113, 174);&quot;&gt;xQueueOverwrite&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 10.4276pt; font-family: Consolas; color: rgb(245, 135, 31);&quot;&gt;( QueueHandle_t xQueue, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 10.4276pt; font-family: Consolas; color: rgb(137, 89, 168);&quot;&gt;const void&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 10.4276pt; font-family: Consolas; color: rgb(245, 135, 31);&quot;&gt; * pvItemToQueue )&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 10.4276pt; font-family: Consolas; color: rgb(77, 77, 76);&quot;&gt;;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(77, 77, 76); font-family: Consolas; font-size: 10.4276pt; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;xQueuePeek( xMailbox, pxData, portMAX_DELAY );&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(77, 77, 76); font-family: Consolas; font-size: 10.4276pt; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;这是不仅仅是API的问题,也是机制的问题,这样方便扩展1个生产者多个消费者可以在同一时刻取到最性的数据&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot; face=&quot;Consolas&quot; color=&quot;#4d4d4c&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.9035px;&quot;&gt;注意&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(66, 113, 174); font-family: Consolas; font-size: 13.9035px;&quot;&gt;xQueueOverwrite 这个API只能使用在队列长度为1的队列中.否则会卡死&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.9035px; color: rgb(66, 113, 174); font-family: Consolas; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;可以使用带时间戳的方式来进行,动作以此来加快进度类似于下面这种形式&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: normal;&quot;&gt;        &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background: 0px 0px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: normal; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid oklch(0.923 0.003 48.717); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline-color: oklab(0.716081 0.00506151 0.00754315 / 0.5); color: rgb(255, 93, 77);&quot; class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;xQueuePeek&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background: 0px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: normal; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid oklch(0.923 0.