quot; class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;邮箱的形式主要适用：因为邮箱,只会检测到数据更新了,但是不知道具体更新了多少,有没有丢包&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid oklch(0.923 0.003 48.717); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline-color: oklab(0.716081 0.00506151 0.00754315 / 0.5); font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; --code-text_v3: #000000d9; --code-doc_v3: #00000073; --code-Link_v3: #2f74ff; --code-number_v3: #e54595; --code-keycontrol_v3: #9952e1; --code-function_v3: #ff5d4d; --code-variable_v3: #000000d9; --code-parameter_v3: #4da621; --code-attributes_v3: #c70; --code-selection-bg-color: #ebf1ff; overflow-wrap: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5; overflow: auto; border-radius: 6px; text-wrap-mode: wrap !important; word-break: break-word !important;&quot; class=&quot;container_7ff80 language-c&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Courier New, monospace&quot; color=&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;邮箱只在乎数据能拿到,我不管你这个是什么数据。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid oklch(0.923 0.003 48.717); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline-color: oklab(0.716081 0.00506151 0.00754315 / 0.5); font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, &amp;quot;SF Mono&amp;quot;, Menlo, Consolas, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, monospace; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-size: 13.6px; --code-text_v3: #000000d9; --code-doc_v3: #00000073; --code-Link_v3: #2f74ff; --code-number_v3: #e54595; --code-keycontrol_v3: #9952e1; --code-function_v3: #ff5d4d; --code-variable_v3: #000000d9; --code-parameter_v3: #4da621; --code-attributes_v3: #c70; --code-selection-bg-color: #ebf1ff; overflow-wrap: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; background: none 0% 0% 